edu.stanford.nlp.pipeline

Class CorefMentionAnnotator

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.stanford.nlp.pipeline.AbstractTextAnnotationCreator
      • edu.stanford.nlp.pipeline.TextAnnotationCreator
        • edu.stanford.nlp.pipeline.CorefMentionAnnotator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AnnotationCreator, Annotator

    public class CorefMentionAnnotator
extends TextAnnotationCreator
implements Annotator
    This class adds mention information to an Annotation. After annotation each sentence will have a List<Mention> representing the Mentions in the sentence. The List<Mention> containing the Mentions will be put under the annotation CorefCoreAnnotations.CorefMentionsAnnotation.
    Author:
    heeyoung, Jason Bolton
